data.description: Lovely Brick House with landscaping.  Don't miss out on this home in Wills Point! Home includes vaulted ceiling in large open concept living room open to kitchen, perfect for entertaining.  Kitchen has island and separate space for eating as well as fireplace in living area.  3 spacious bedrooms and 2 baths. Bathrooms & kitchen recently updated with ceramic tile floor. Huge backyard, with storage bldg., perfect for all activities.  You will enjoy how quite and convenient this neighborhood is.
